{
  "id": "adv_bond_ai_01_04",
  "title": "小美山愛4",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "（トレーニングに夢中になってたら）\n（あっという間に暗くなっちゃった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was so engrossed in my training）\n（It got dark so quickly…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 5.7000002861
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "（はーあ、日が落ちるのも早くなってきたし）\n（明日からはもう少し早くジムを出るようにしよう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Haaー‚ the sun is setting earlier）\n（so let's leave the gym a little earlier starting tomorrow）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7000002861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 14.3666662533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "（暗い所って昔から苦手なんだよな……）\n（ん……？　背後からなんか変な足音がしてる……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I've never been able to get used to dark places…）\n（Hmm…? I think I hear some strange footsteps behind me…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3666662533,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-03.m4a",
          "delay": 5000.000699499999
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-03.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.6673661999985
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.4666669528
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.4333321571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃん……タスケテ……愛ちゃん……タスケテ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan… HELP ME… Ai-chan… HELP ME…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333321571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "（な、何この声！？）\n（そういえばこの間こころから怖い話を聞いたような……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（W-What's with that voice!?）\n（Think about it‚ I remember hearing a scary story from Kokoro a while ago…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3666665076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "（『夜道を一人で歩いている時に、ペタペタって足音が）\n（後ろから付いてきて名前を呼ばれたらヤバイ』って……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She said \"When you’re walking alone at night‚ if you hear footsteps）\n（behind you or someone calls your name‚ it’s dangerous\"…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3000006038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.9000006038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "（わー、なんでこんな時に怖い話を）\n（思い出しちゃうの！？　私のバカバカバカーっ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Whoaー‚ why do I think of scary story at a time）\n（like this!? I'm fool fool foolー!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9000006038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "（あー、ダメダメ、何も考えないようにしないと……）\n（考えるな、考えるな、考えるな、考えるな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ahー‚ no no‚ I have to try not to think about anything…）\n（Don't think‚ don't think‚ don't think‚ don't think…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.1333324113,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7066.667429499994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.1999998408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "（ひぃっ！？　草むらがなんか動いた！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Eeek!? Something moved in the bushes!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1999998408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "待って……逃げんといて……愛ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait… Don't run away… Ai-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9999998408,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14933.332729499994
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "（うう……私は何も見てないし、聞いてない！）\n（もう嫌だ……よし、寮まで走って帰ろう……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ugh… I didn't see or hear anything!）\n（I can't stand this anymore… right‚ run back to the dorm…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9333331742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-night",
      "startTime": 79.8882259049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……はあ……はあ……やっと寮についた……\nジムの後のダッシュはさすがに少し辛いな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… haa… I finally arrived at the dorm…\nRunning after the gym is a bit hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0333341914,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12800.007629500002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.7833418209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "ただいまー\nあれ……？　今日は誰もいないのかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm backー\nOh…? Is there anyone here today…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8333418209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "（な、何……！？　急に電気がついたり消えたり……）\n（ま、まさか……幽霊が寮まで付いてきた！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（W-What…!? The lights are suddenly going on and off…）\n（N-No way… A ghost followed me to the dorm!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.5333418209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.4333418209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "やだやだやだ……幽霊さん……ごめんなさい……\n私何もしてないですよぉ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nonono… Mr‚ Ghost… I'm sorry…\nI didn't do anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4333418209,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12349.958896600001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃん……愛ちゃん……愛ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan… Ai-chan… Ai-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3333418209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0000053406
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5333413123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーーーーーーっ！　触れないで下さいっ！\nごめんなさい、ごめんなさいぃっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aaーーーーーーah! Don't touch me!\nI'm sorry‚ I'm sorryー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5333413123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.4333413123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃん！　うちよ！　鈴村優です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai-chan! It's me! Yu Suzumura!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4333413123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.6666746456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "はあはあ……なんだ……優ちゃんだったんですね……\n良かったです……幽霊じゃなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa-haa… Oh… It's Yu-chan…\nI'm so glad… It wasn't a ghost…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6666746456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.2333413123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "酷いわぁ……。廊下の照明が調子悪くて電球を\n買いに行った帰りに愛ちゃんを発見したんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's too much… The hallway light was weird‚ so I went to buy a new bulb\nand found Ai-chan on my way back",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2333413123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "声掛けようと思って近づいたら\n全力で走って逃げるんやもん。びっくりしたわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but when I approached you to talk to you‚\nyou ran away as fast as you could‚ I'm so surprised~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.700007979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.700007979
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_ai_01_04-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんね……本当に怖かったんだもん……\nでも『助けて』なんて言って近づかれたら怖いよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm so sorry… I'm really scared…\nBut it's scary when you come near and says‚ \"Help me\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.700007979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.4333413123
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
